article.headline: Morgan St. 76, East Carolina 70
article.story: BALTIMORE (AP) -- Jamar Smith scored a game-high 22 points and grabbed 7 rebounds, and Morgan State defeated East Carolina 76-70 Monday night. Joseph McLean contributed 19 points and added three rebounds for Morgan (1-6). Ronald Timus and Boubacar Coly each added seven rebounds. Darrell Jenkins scored a team-high 18 points and grabbed three rebounds for East Carolina (4-4).
